						<summary>

						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1574 (1652 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>States that Rāmānuja-Mahāmuni constructed the <hi rend="italic">Yajñaśāla-(maṇḍapa)</hi> in the temple. The record is in Sanskrit verse written in Telugu characters. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1574,</hi> expressed by the chronogram <hi rend="italic">Vasumatyē,</hi> <hi rend="bold">Nandana, Vaiśākha śu. bhadrā, Atithi,</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1652 A.D.,</hi> April 5, <hi rend="bold">Monday; śu. (7).</hi></p>						

						</summary>
