<p>1. The following short inscription is engraved on a pillar in the maṇḍapa. 1 taṁjaAḷa 2 giyamaṇa 3 vāḷidāsu- 4 lu sadāśēva [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*]</p>

